1. Synthetix announced an emergency plan for sUSD depegging;
2. SkyAI, the first pre-sale project of the Four.Meme platform, has raised more than 25 million US dollars;
3. OM CEO: Details of the destruction plan will be announced soon, and the buyback is still in progress;
4. Analysis shows that BTC's rise from $70,000 to $110,000 lacks retail participation, and the trend may be similar to the end of 2021;
5. Canary submitted an application for Staked TRX ETF;
6. The main culprit of Brazil's largest crypto scam was sentenced to 128 years, and the three people were sentenced to a total of more than 170 years;
7. The Aptos community proposal proposes to reduce the annualized return on staking by nearly 50% to improve capital efficiency;
8. Backpack has issued points for the fourth week of the first season today;
9. Multiple Meme coins suddenly crashed, suspected whales or groups were liquidated;
10. Binance Research: The record issuance of US Treasury bonds may increase macro pressure on the crypto market;
11. Cardano The founder responded to not being invited by the White House: No need to make a deal with Trump;
12. Coinbase criticized Oregon for trying to restart the "law enforcement instead of legislation" crypto regulatory model.
